  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dba\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0d9f \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel is scarce again",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Shanta Silva, joint secretary of Ceylon Petroleum Private Tanker Owners Association, says that stocks of both diesel and petrol are not available.",
        "As a result, there has been a shortage of fuel across the country, the secretary said.",
        "Mr. Shanta Silva mentioned that many filling stations have been closed due to lack of fuel and long queues have formed again near some filling stations."
      ],
